You are working on **CULTR Health**, a HIPAA-compliant telehealth platform for
GLP-1 weight loss medications, wellness peptides, and longevity optimization.

- Production: https://cultrhealth.com (waitlist, `production` branch)
- Staging: https://staging.cultrhealth.com (full app, `staging` branch)
