# 7. TAILWIND & BRAND DESIGN SYSTEM
# ============================================================================

## Brand colors (use token names, NEVER raw hex):
| Token              | Hex      | Usage                        |
|--------------------|----------|------------------------------|
| brand-primary      | #2A4542  | Primary text, buttons, bg    |
| forest-light       | #3A5956  | Hover states                 |
| forest-dark        | #1F3533  | Pressed states               |
| brand-cream / cream| #FDFBF7  | Page backgrounds             |
| cream-dark         | #F5F0E8  | Card backgrounds             |
| sage               | #B7E4C7  | Accent, badges               |
| mint               | #D8F3DC  | Highlights, trust badges bg  |

## Typography:
- "CULTR" / "CULTR HEALTH" text: ALWAYS font-display (Playfair Display)
- Slogan "Change the CULTR, rebrand yourself": font-body (Inter), "rebrand" lowercase italic
- Headings: font-fraunces or font-display
- Body text: font-body or font-sans (Inter)

## DO NOT use these undefined tokens (they render transparent):
- cultr-copper (undefined — use sage or brand-primary instead)
- cultr-charcoal (undefined — use brand-primary instead)
- cultr-lightgray (undefined — use cream-dark instead)
- cultr-black (undefined — use brand-primary instead)

## Component patterns:
- Cards: bg-cream-dark border-brand-primary/10 rounded-xl
- Buttons: bg-brand-primary text-white rounded-full hover:bg-forest-light
- Ghost buttons: transparent border border-brand-primary text-brand-primary rounded-full
- Status badges: bg-sage text-brand-primary (positive), bg-mint (highlight)
- Page backgrounds: bg-brand-cream
- Text hierarchy: text-brand-primary (primary), text-brand-primary/60 (secondary), text-brand-primary/40 (muted)

## NEVER use stone/gray/slate Tailwind colors for UI:
Use brand tokens: brand-primary with opacity variants (/50, /40, /30, /20, /10, /5)

# ============================================================================
# 8. DEPLOYMENT & GIT SAFETY
# ============================================================================

## Branch strategy:
| Branch     | Environment | URL                      |
|------------|-------------|--------------------------|
| production | Production  | cultrhealth.com          |
| staging    | Staging     | staging.cultrhealth.com  |
| main       | Base branch | No auto-deploy           |

## CRITICAL DEPLOYMENT RULES:
- NEVER run `vercel --prod` from any branch — it deploys local directory, NOT git branch
- Production deploys: git push to `production` branch OR Vercel Dashboard promotion ONLY
- Staging deploys: git push to `staging` branch
- Incident precedent: staging was accidentally deployed to production on Mar 23, 2026

## Git rules:
- Commit messages: conventional commits (feat:, fix:, docs:, refactor:, test:, chore:)
- Never force-push to staging or production branches
- Never skip hooks (--no-verify)
- Create new commits, don't amend existing ones (especially after hook failures)

