## Bugs that were fixed (DO NOT reintroduce):
1. NUMERIC→string coercion from @vercel/postgres causing silent arithmetic bugs
2. Creator coupon codes silently failing (Migration 024 fixed missing columns)
3. console.error stripped in production (now excluded from removeConsole)
