5. Email logos breaking on localhost (fixed with getEmailSiteUrl() helper)
6. Hydration errors from <button> inside <button> (fixed with div + role="button")
7. SQL CAST(${string} AS INTERVAL) failing with prepared statements
8. UNION ALL with duplicate param indices in @vercel/postgres

