# ============================================================================
# 14. MIDDLEWARE & ROUTING
# ============================================================================

## middleware.ts handles:
- Subdomain rewriting: join.* root path (`/`) → `/join` internally; non-root join paths pass through unchanged
- HIPAA no-cache headers on authenticated routes
- Content-Security-Policy headers
- Camera/microphone permissions for consultation video routes
- Pass-through for: /r/ tracking links, /api/ routes, static assets

## LayoutShell hides Header/Footer on:
- /creators/portal/*
- /admin/*
- /join-club/*

## Route redirects (in next.config.js):
- /products → /pricing (301)
- /library → /members (301)
- /library/* → /members/* (301)
- /consultations/* → /members/consultations/* (301)

