# ============================================================================
# 23. SELF-CORRECTING RULE
# ============================================================================

Every time the AI gets something wrong about this project — a wrong file path,
incorrect assumption, outdated pattern, misunderstood convention — the correction
should be added to CLAUDE.md so it persists across future sessions. Do not just
fix inline; codify the fix.
